Horizontal mirroring for horizontal scrolling allows raster effects such as raising the weapon menu out of the floor, or a rising and falling ceiling or floor. See also the first fortress in SMB3.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=9">tepples</a> — Sat May 19, 2012 5:43 am</p><hr />
